Service Mesh

Monitor and manage secure, reliable services

Unlock fully managed, observable, and secure communication across your fleet services. Create a fleet to get started. Learn about Service Mesh

What are fleets?

Manage, observe, and secure your services without changing your application code

Understand your applications: Gain deep insights into service performance and proactively catch issues with fleet-wide tracing, monitoring, and logging.

Simplify security: Embrace a zero-trust model by automatically and declaratively securing service communication.

Easily manage traffic: Control traffic flows and API calls between services while gaining critical visibility into your network.
